# Baseline: every text file is stored LF, repository-wide. Not only the
# runner-critical extensions — a CRLF-only diff on a file nobody touched hides
# the real changes in review and puts noise into a tagged history.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicit, because these two also matter at runtime: this repository's product
# is shell inside YAML, and a CRLF line ending in a run block reaches a Linux
# runner as a literal carriage return and breaks the script.
*.yml text eol=lf
*.toml text eol=lf

# Explicit for documentation, which is most of this repository.
*.md text eol=lf
